Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.32,0:01:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞爾，晚飯好像快好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你決定了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.03,0:01:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我陪伴你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子該結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻的魔力已經變得相當的強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.49,0:02:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣她一定可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.66,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們再不來吃，燉肉會冷掉的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我馬上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.43,0:02:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我辛辛苦苦煮給你們吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果艾瑞爾與斯比都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看，你們看，你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.13,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第68話 小櫻與過去的庫洛里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.22,0:03:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，這些雪是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能光顧著逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想辦法對付雪人們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛創造的庫洛牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄舊有姿態\N重新轉生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以新主人，小櫻之名命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「雪」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.28,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪啊，把他們都埋起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次小櫻又解決了問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請加油，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一套新的戰鬥服\N本來想讓妳穿上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次發生什麼怪事時\N妳一定一定要穿上喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.04,0:05:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果怪事接二連三的發生\N我也會很困擾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有妳在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊\N妳克服了許多難題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把庫洛牌都變成小櫻牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.76,0:06:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好小櫻可以變成\N比庫洛還了不起的魔法師喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼你也這麼想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，還早得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要追上庫洛，還差一大截
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.14,0:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說話幹嘛那麼認真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，妳睡不著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可\N庫洛先生是什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼突然這麼問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.55,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你們也說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.09,0:07:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我現在的魔力\N不管什麼事都能應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.46,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，月說我還差一大截
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月會那麼在意庫洛\N是有其他的原因啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會想起庫洛先生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.07,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，他的確很令人難忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的主人是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還不像庫洛先生\N那樣魔力高強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.49,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生怪事時\N也只能拼命的設法解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果是庫洛先生\N一定不會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我當你們的新主人真的好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛是庫洛，妳是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.08,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他比沒有意義\N也不需要跟他比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.02,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了，別想那些了\N快睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的雪下得真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那天一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，被妳聽到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你一直提起庫洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我不禁想起他死時的情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生？\N對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.76,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是這個季節\N那天也下著這種大雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前他一直很健康的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他突然說\N“我的壽命已盡，所以今天要分離了”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人連臨死前都好自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我總覺得他還活著\N到現在還在捉弄著我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，為什麼眼睛睜得那麼大？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.48,0:09:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說庫洛先生\N或許還活著，說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的，開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛死時我跟月都在他身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼\N每次發生怪事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會感覺到庫洛先生的氣息呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.04,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好庫洛死前做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見他，確定這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去見誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.42,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用「回」牌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要回到過去的世界\N直接去問庫洛先生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就可以了解最近的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是使用回牌\N會消耗很多的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一中途發生什麼事的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可說只要借助\N月峰神社的櫻樹的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能夠有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還是太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「回」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要小心一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會回來，打鉤鉤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.91,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打鉤鉤，說謊的人會被千根針扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼待會兒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請送我到\N庫洛先生死去前的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？可魯貝洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是月啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是只有這棵櫻樹還沒有開花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快是什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹真的會開花嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可跟月在做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，你太多事了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可跟月好像很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個好像都很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳睡飽了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很涼，最適合睡午覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.21,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的，我想請教您一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是從未來來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想問我的事是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了一些…一些怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後每次我都會感覺到您的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.53,0:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想\N會不會是你做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說我做了就有做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說我沒做我就沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.88,0:15:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛，我不是叫你\N不要用泡牌幫我洗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的感情真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不喜歡這些孩子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然最喜歡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小可、月\N還有庫洛牌們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.88,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是我畢竟不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下，庫洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來夏天已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季節似乎很自然地在交替著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.38,0:16:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有想過\N那種悲傷的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就跟\N令人感覺到季節交替的落葉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張椅子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.06,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得跟艾瑞爾家的椅子一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快解釋，庫洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我說的意思啊，月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要離開這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.21,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個笑話不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾，這並不是笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的壽命已盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壽命？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你的脾氣古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過庫洛里德是\N全世界最厲害的魔法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你創造出來的我們\N最清楚這點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.76,0:17:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此\N萬物都一樣有壽終的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也必須做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.10,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備一個在我之後\N可以仁慈待你們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要別的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由你決定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.02,0:18:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看那個人\N適不適合當你們的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會適合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有月一個人決定也不公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,候補人選由可魯貝洛斯來決定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.23,0:18:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月、可魯貝洛斯以及庫洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我傾全部心血及力量\N創造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我希望在我死後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.51,0:18:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也能在新主人身邊\N幸福的過日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.38,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最後的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.99,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像季節不斷交替一樣\N人也是會不斷地交替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是活在這世上的人\N真正的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小可跟月怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要妳當他們的新主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我恐怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，妳一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.06,0:19:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有辦法變成你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小可跟月的那種感情\N不會輸給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.54,0:19:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算那樣\N我仍然不是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.92,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是妳，絕對不會變成我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.99,0:19:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳只要在妳的時間內\N努力的活下去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.30,0:20:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的事是無法改變或消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.10,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，未來永遠在妳的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，冬天已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的春天開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.33,0:20:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攤開看不見的地圖尋找方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.84,0:20:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的光輝正在某處等著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.68,0:20:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充滿噪音的都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.68,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要無法呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.02,0:21:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中時間不斷的流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要保持純真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將靈感拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.21,0:21:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷失於迷宮時雖會感到迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攤開看不見的地圖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是我，妳是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.16,0:21:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳擁有只有妳才能描繪的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.98,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？\N知道什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳沒見到庫洛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.49,0:22:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我見到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我沒有問他\N最近發生的究竟是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.80,0:22:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳是去做什麼的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說也奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.60,0:22:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛先生他們\N為什麼會在艾瑞爾家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞爾？妳是說妳的同學嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.24,0:22:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能，庫洛死的地方是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.18,0:22:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，是在什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.02,0:22:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.98,0:22:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於那部分的記憶好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.49,0:22:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月也曾經到過艾瑞爾家\N可是他什麼也沒說耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記憶被消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，是誰幹的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是庫洛里德的傑作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.44,0:23:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.65,0:23:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這一世的名字叫艾瑞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.48,0:23:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而前世的名字叫庫洛里德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.47,0:24:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？大家都因為\N艾瑞爾的魔法而睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.50,0:24:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在天亮前無法破解魔法陣\N大家會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.07,0:24:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.81,0:24:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.04,0:24:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛魔法使\N「小櫻與現身的庫洛里德」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.48,0:24:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也與小櫻一起\N解除封印！
